F.I.E.S.T.A.Faculty Interaction & Engagement with Students Through fun
Activities

Greetings folks!

To augment the bonding between students and the faculty of insti, Saathi
brings to you, F.I.E.S.T.A., an event first of its kind.

F.I.E.S.T.A is a mini-mela with fun activities and food stalls
=E2=80=8B where students and faculty will come together to participate, eat=
 and
have a fun-and-frolic-filled Saturday with games like
'Eating Competition' , 'Karaoke' , 'Do Not Laugh!'

